<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Hotefinder c'est quoi?</p>
      <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Spécialiste de la mise en relation entre Propriétaire et prestataire de service de proximité.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
      <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-y-16">
        <div class="relative text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-600">
            <svg class="h-10 w-10 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
